httpx-sse (0.4.3-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of httpx-sse 0.4.3 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of mcp (Avalan's `server` extras). Not in
    Debian or Noble, so hand-package from the upstream PyPI sdist.
  * Pure Python with zero runtime dependencies. Build is a vanilla
    pybuild/pyproject run against setuptools; the version is resolved
    from ``httpx_sse.__version__`` via setuptools' attr backend, so
    no setuptools-scm git probe is required.

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Tue, 19 May 2026 10:00:00 -0300
